        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--video表</span><br><span class="line">create external table video_ori(</span><br><span class="line">videoId string,</span><br><span class="line">uploader string,</span><br><span class="line">age int,</span><br><span class="line">category array&lt;string&gt;,</span><br><span class="line">length int,</span><br><span class="line">views int,</span><br><span class="line">rate float,</span><br><span class="line">ratings int,</span><br><span class="line">comments int,</span><br><span class="line">relatedId array&lt;string&gt;)</span><br><span class="line">row format delimited fields terminated by "\t"</span><br><span class="line">collection items terminated by "&amp;"</span><br><span class="line">location '/gulivideo/video';</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--user表</span><br><span class="line">create external table user_ori(</span><br><span class="line">uplodaer string,</span><br><span class="line">videos int,</span><br><span class="line">friends int)</span><br><span class="line">row format delimited</span><br><span class="line">fields terminated by "\t"</span><br><span class="line">location '/gulivideo/user';</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--video_orc表</span><br><span class="line">create table video_orc(</span><br><span class="line">videoId string,</span><br><span class="line">uploader string,</span><br><span class="line">age int,</span><br><span class="line">category array&lt;string&gt;,</span><br><span class="line">length int,</span><br><span class="line">views int,</span><br><span class="line">rate float,</span><br><span class="line">ratings int,</span><br><span class="line">comments int,</span><br><span class="line">relatedId array&lt;string&gt;)</span><br><span class="line">stored as orc</span><br><span class="line">tblproperties("orc.compress"="SNAPPY");</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--user_orc表</span><br><span class="line">create table user_orc(</span><br><span class="line">uploader string,</span><br><span class="line">video int,</span><br><span class="line">friends int)</span><br><span class="line">stored as orc</span><br><span class="line">tblproperties("orc.compress"="SNAPPY");</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--从外部表中插入数据</span><br><span class="line">insert into table video_orc select * from video_ori;</span><br><span class="line">insert into table user_orc select * from user_ori;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id="1-统计视频观看数top10"><a href="#1-统计视频观看数top10" class="headerlink" title="1.统计视频观看数top10"></a>1.统计视频观看数top10</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select </span><br><span class="line">videoId,views</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">video_orc</span><br><span class="line">order by</span><br><span class="line">views desc</span><br><span class="line">limit 10;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id="2-统计视频类别热度top10"><a href="#2-统计视频类别热度top10" class="headerlink" title="2.统计视频类别热度top10"></a>2.统计视频类别热度top10</h2><p>1.定义视频类别热度（假设按照类别下视频的个数来决定）</p><p>2.炸开类别(t1)</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">videoId,cate</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">video_orc lateral view explode(category) tbl as cate;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>3.统计各个类别有多少视频，并取排序前十</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">cate,</span><br><span class="line">count(videoId) n</span><br><span class="line">from </span><br><span class="line">t1</span><br><span class="line">group by cate</span><br><span class="line">order by </span><br><span class="line">n desc</span><br><span class="line">limit 2;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id="3-统计出视频观看数最高的20个视频的所属类别以及类别包含top20视频的个数"><a href="#3-统计出视频观看数最高的20个视频的所属类别以及类别包含top20视频的个数" class="headerlink" title="3.统计出视频观看数最高的20个视频的所属类别以及类别包含top20视频的个数"></a>3.统计出视频观看数最高的20个视频的所属类别以及类别包含top20视频的个数</h2><p>1.统计前20视频和其类别</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">videoid,views,category</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">video_orc</span><br><span class="line">order by</span><br><span class="line">views desc</span><br><span class="line">limit 20;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>2.打散类别</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">videoid,cate</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">t1 lateral view expplode(category) tbl as cate;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>3.按照类别统计个数</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">cate,count(videoid) n</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">t2</span><br><span class="line">group by</span><br><span class="line">cate</span><br><span class="line">order by</span><br><span class="line">n desc;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id="4-统计视频观看数top50所关联视频的所属类别排序"><a href="#4-统计视频观看数top50所关联视频的所属类别排序" class="headerlink" title="4.统计视频观看数top50所关联视频的所属类别排序"></a>4.统计视频观看数top50所关联视频的所属类别排序</h2><p>1.统计观看数前50的视频的关联视频</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">videoid,views,relatedid</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">video_orc</span><br><span class="line">order by</span><br><span class="line">views desc</span><br><span class="line">limit 50;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>2.炸开关联视频</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">explode(relatedid) videoid</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">t1;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>3.和原表join获取类别</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">distinct t2.videoid,</span><br><span class="line">v.category</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">t2</span><br><span class="line">join video_orc v on</span><br><span class="line">t2.videoid=v.videoid;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>4.炸开类别</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">explode(category) cate</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">t3;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>5.和类别热度表(t5)join，排序</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">distinct t4.cate,t5.n</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">t4</span><br><span class="line">join t5 on</span><br><span class="line">t4.cate=t5.cate</span><br><span class="line">order by</span><br><span class="line">t5.n desc;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id="5-统计每个类别中的视频热度top10，以music为例"><a href="#5-统计每个类别中的视频热度top10，以music为例" class="headerlink" title="5.统计每个类别中的视频热度top10，以music为例"></a>5.统计每个类别中的视频热度top10，以music为例</h2><p>1.把视频表的类别炸开</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">create table video_category</span><br><span class="line">stored as orc TBLPROPERTIES("orc.compress"="SNAPPY") as select</span><br><span class="line">videoid,uploader,age,cate,length,views,rate,ratings,comments,relatedid</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">video_orc</span><br><span class="line">lateral view explode(category) tbl as cate limit 100;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>2.从video_category直接查询music类的前10视频</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">videoid,views </span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">video_category</span><br><span class="line">where</span><br><span class="line">cate="Music"</span><br><span class="line">order by</span><br><span class="line">views desc</span><br><span class="line">limit 10;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id="6-统计每个类别中视频流量top10，以music为例"><a href="#6-统计每个类别中视频流量top10，以music为例" class="headerlink" title="6.统计每个类别中视频流量top10，以music为例"></a>6.统计每个类别中视频流量top10，以music为例</h2><p>1.从video_category直接查阅Music类的流量前10视频</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">videoid,ratings</span><br><span class="line">from </span><br><span class="line">video_category</span><br><span class="line">where</span><br><span class="line">cate="Music"</span><br><span class="line">order by</span><br><span class="line">ratings desc</span><br><span class="line">limit 10;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id="7-统计上传视频最多的用户top10以及他们上传的观看次数在前20的视频"><a href="#7-统计上传视频最多的用户top10以及他们上传的观看次数在前20的视频" class="headerlink" title="7.统计上传视频最多的用户top10以及他们上传的观看次数在前20的视频"></a>7.统计上传视频最多的用户top10以及他们上传的观看次数在前20的视频</h2><h4 id="理解一：前10用户每人前20："><a href="#理解一：前10用户每人前20：" class="headerlink" title="理解一：前10用户每人前20："></a>理解一：前10用户每人前20：</h4><p>1.统计视频上传最多的用户top10</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">uploader,video</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">user_orc</span><br><span class="line">order by</span><br><span class="line">video desc</span><br><span class="line">limit 10;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>2.与video_orc联立，找出这些用户上传的视频，并按照热度排名</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">t1.uploader,v.videoid,rank() over(partition by t1.uploader order by v.views desc) hot</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">t1</span><br><span class="line">left join video_orc v on</span><br><span class="line">t1.uploder=v.uploader;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>3.求每个人的前20</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">t2.uploader,t2.videoid,t2.hot</span><br><span class="line">from t2</span><br><span class="line">where</span><br><span class="line">hot&lt;=20;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h4 id="理解二：前10用户总榜前20"><a href="#理解二：前10用户总榜前20" class="headerlink" title="理解二：前10用户总榜前20"></a>理解二：前10用户总榜前20</h4><p>1.统计视频上传最多用户top10</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">uploader,video</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">user_orc</span><br><span class="line">order by</span><br><span class="line">video desc</span><br><span class="line">limit 10;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>2.观看前20的视频</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">videoid,uploader,views</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">video_orc</span><br><span class="line">order by</span><br><span class="line">views desc</span><br><span class="line">limit 20;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>3.联立两表，看看有没有他们上传的</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">t1.uploader,t2.videoid</span><br><span class="line">from t1</span><br><span class="line">left join t2 on</span><br><span class="line">t1.uploader=t2.uploader;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id="8-统计每个类别视频观看数top10"><a href="#8-统计每个类别视频观看数top10" class="headerlink" title="8.统计每个类别视频观看数top10"></a>8.统计每个类别视频观看数top10</h2><p>1.从video_category表查出每个类别视频观看数排名</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">cate,videoid,views,rank() over(partition by cate order by views desc) hot</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">video_category;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>2.取每个类别的top10</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">select</span><br><span class="line">cate,videoid,views</span><br><span class="line">from t1</span><br><span class="line">where</span><br><span class="line">hot&lt;=10;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
